9df-ccdc-400f-ace2-b5bc42b3605c"}]},{"response":"For scheme network, SSC delivered the migration of UnionPay International (UPI) Acquiring System of the leading UPI acquirer to the Indirect System from the Direct System in Thailand.  It was achieved without the need to modify the POS software of the UPI Direct System.  Since then, the system has been enhanced with QR support, and a purchase payment paid via multiple UPI cards., @4bde50e6-849a-445b-867e-595121ae21bc?","attr":{"x":2890,"y":572,"isQuestion":false,"id":"4bde50e6-849a-445b-867e-595121ae21bc"},"hooks":[{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"เลือก"},{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"@39729889-9fcb-412d-b2a6-7c7cd2af5afc"}]},{"response":"For a cost effective Call Centre and/or Helpdesk solution iServiceDesks, SSC offers both software and Cloud hosting services for timely deployment., @75eab958-2320-4142-8206-eb74f5bb371c?","attr":{"x":2848,"y":312,"isQuestion":false,"id":"75eab958-2320-4142-8206-eb74f5bb371c"},"hooks":[{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"เลือก"},{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"@5cdeacbd-0fa4-4709-a6a2-3a4fdef78392"}]},{"response":"https://www.iservicedesks.com, @13c88cd7-2e91-4378-b043-0398bd121725?","attr":{"x":3716,"y":337,"isQuestion":false,"id":"13c88cd7-2e91-4378-b043-0398bd121725"},"hooks":[{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"@75eab958-2320-4142-8206-eb74f5bb371c"}]},{"response":"For electronic bill presentment and payment, SSC is the Thai partner of ebpSource, the leading EBPP solution provider.  ebpSource delivered the first very successful transaction banking EBPP to a major Thai bank in the early 2000s in Thailand., @ec7b2200-19de-4b5d-b1b9-33cf00ad695e?","attr":{"x":2851,"y":227,"isQuestion":false,"id":"ec7b2200-19de-4b5d-b1b9-33cf00ad695e"},"hooks":[{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"เลือก"},{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"@652826b0-a8b4-49df-b25f-ffe732d73235"}]},{"response":"To secure pin entry for mobile and Internet payment application, SSC offers a cost effective and secured virtual Pin Pad solution. \nIn addition to secure pin entry as part of the authentication process, SSC offers Facial Recognition implementation for different types of application., @c71ff642-e264-44cf-9363-c46fafb9ff51?","attr":{"x":2895,"y":657,"isQuestion":false,"id":"c71ff642-e264-44cf-9363-c46fafb9ff51"},"hooks":[{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"เลือก"},{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"@541157dc-8b74-4798-852e-675e26803e17"}]},{"response":", @c266383a-39b1-4af0-838b-13f830d9fcf2 #target?","attr":{"x":118,"y":617,"isQuestion":false,"id":"c266383a-39b1-4af0-838b-13f830d9fcf2"},"hooks":[{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"@5c4eff12-61d1-45c2-add9-9b1841fa7015"}]},{"response":", @e8c0a8fe-b64d-48d3-91a1-4e12cdd2b125?","attr":{"x":250,"y":547,"isQuestion":false,"id":"e8c0a8fe-b64d-48d3-91a1-4e12cdd2b125"},"hooks":[{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"#target"},{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"@c266383a-39b1-4af0-838b-13f830d9fcf2"}]},{"response":", @7507ceaa-ed52-4822-858e-d8a08af3ee17 `post://Content-Type=application/x-www-form-urlencoded&charset=UTF-8://message=%1&sessionId=#tokenId://#target`?","attr":{"x":254,"y":668,"isQuestion":false,"id":"7507ceaa-ed52-4822-858e-d8a08af3ee17"},"hooks":[{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"@c266383a-39b1-4af0-838b-13f830d9fcf2"}]},{"response":"%2","attr":{"x":417,"y":670,"id":"0e80d096-6221-4514-b068-b6cf5630507d"},"hooks":[{"match":"Words","weight":1,"text":"@7507ceaa-ed52-4822-858e-d8a08af3ee17"}]},{"response":"#aka\n#position\n#why\n#salary\n#portfolio","attr":{"x":1964,"y":1532,"id":"eb1927c5-0db3-47a8-8835-9f780618bbbc"},"hooks":[]}],"greeting":", @f4bfb6e1-f596-41b5-800a-f54d280d2ae8?","language":"TH","title":"คุยกับ TWK บอท","attr":{"start":{"x":100,"y":100,"isQuestion":false,"id":"f4bfb6e1-f596-41b5-800a-f54d280d2ae8"},"silent":{"x":100,"y":300,"isQuestion":false,"id":"068a6a20-b1cd-4d1a-81f9-643a7c2257ad"},"end":{"x":100,"y":200,"isQuestion":false,"id":"5c4eff12-61d1-45c2-add9-9b1841fa7015"},"connectio